    Welcome to the WDTB website. Use the navigation links at the top and
   bottom of each page or the buttons to the left to get around the site.
                    The main areas are described below...


   Weather Event Simulator Training ~
   Register Now.
   News ~
   Updated January 24, 2002!
   Latest happenings at WDTB! Support ~
   Support for WDTB products, including CD-ROMs and teletraining.
   WDTB Forum ~
   Log on to our threaded discussion forum! Site Map ~
   Links to every major page on the site.
   Schedules ~
   Our latest course schedules. About WDTB ~
   Who we are and what we do.
   Courses ~
   Information about our course offerings. Feedback ~
   Send an email feedback message to the Webmaster and the WDTB admin
   staff.
   Resources ~
   All training resources, including presentations, papers. Contact ~
   Email, Snail Mail, Phone Numbers and other contact information!
   Links ~
   Interesting links to external sites.
